{"id":113649,"type":2,"name":"Flowers and Trees","name_cn":"花与树","date":"1932-07-30","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/2e/52/113649_v8q88.jpg","rating":{"rank":3257,"total":96,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":2,"5":6,"6":29,"7":40,"8":13,"9":2,"10":2},"score":6.7},"summary":"　　本片1932年获得奥斯卡最佳动画短片奖。 \r\n　　清晨，森林中的花儿、树儿、鸟儿从睡梦中醒来，舒展腰肢梳洗打扮，准备充实愉快地度过崭新的一天。自然，枯干的老树桩也醒了过来，不过他可不觉得生活有什么美好，睁开眼即不耐烦地驱赶他身旁的花儿、鸟儿。见男树正向女树浪漫地求爱，他不由分说强行将女树揽入怀中，男树见状，起身与他决定，老树桩败下阵来。不甘心的老树桩心生毒计，没料想遭殃的是他自己。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>花与树</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>製作: </span><a href=\"/person/6816\">Walt Disney Pictures</a></li><li><span>上映年度: </span>1932-07-30</li><li><span>片长: </span>8 分钟</li><li><span>导演: </span>Burt Gillett</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0022899</li>","collection":{"on_hold":5,"dropped":6,"wish":11,"collect":153,"doing":3},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":49},{"name":"欧美","count":35},{"name":"迪士尼","count":26},{"name":"Disney","count":20},{"name":"美国","count":9},{"name":"欢乐","count":7},{"name":"奥斯卡","count":5},{"name":"原创","count":5},{"name":"剧场版","count":2},{"name":"美国动画","count":2},{"name":"2021","count":1},{"name":"动物","count":1},{"name":"undefined","count":1},{"name":"音乐","count":1},{"name":"子供向","count":1},{"name":"经典","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":913608,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/913608","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""}],"staff":[{"id":6816,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/4f/85/6816_prsn_MGpfY.jpg","name":"Walt Disney Pictures","desc":"製作"}]}